# 🍽 Food Restaurant Website

A simple and clean responsive food ordering website made using HTML and CSS.

## 🔥 Features
- Responsive design
- Food menu showcase
- Customer review section
- Contact form
- 50% offer banner

## 🚀 Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
-JavaScript

